{
  "stem": "18626.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 387.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when I heard the machine guns, and then other cattle trains, some other people had the same idea too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When they came to the forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not only we had idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Other young people had the same idea too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when it was a lot of shooting, the train stopped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Germans stopped the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They opened up the doors from the cattle train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They walked in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They pushed themselves in, because it's so loaded that it was hard for two, three people to go in there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We all had to stand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was no place to sit down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they took out from each cattle train like three, four people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They laid them down in the side of the railroad, and they killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they said, everybody to the trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they opened up the gate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were driving off to Germany in the train-- in the cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother stood a little by the door too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And further up she say another boy dragging in who was shot from far away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She didn't-- and it looked like me a little, too, like a blond skinny guy like me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She start hysterically crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My brother and sister couldn't stop helping crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she says, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Morris is dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I saw him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were dragging him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were dragging him in in the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He's there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I know Maishke's head.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I know that's him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Children said, no, that was not him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was another guy who looks-- boy who looks like Maishke.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And to that day, I feel very sorry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because my mother died [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in her mind that I was shot at that transport.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was in the other cattle trains there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
